OL,3,CWhy Starmer picked Mandelson for
OL,4,CWashington
OL,6,FHere are a few more thoughts about
OL,7,FMandelson's appointment to be the UK's
OL,8,Fperson in Washington.
OL,10,FFirst, as I said on News at Ten last
OL,11,Fnight, this is as important an
OL,12,Fappointment as to a very senior
OL,13,Fcabinet post, because Trump will be
OL,14,Fthe most consequential US president of
OL,15,Four age, for the UK and the whole
OL,16,Fworld.
