OL,3,CWhy Starmer picked Mandelson for
OL,4,CWashington
OL,6,FWithin hours of Trump's inauguration
OL,7,Fon 20 January, the new British
OL,8,Fambassador will have to make the case
OL,9,Fagainst Trump's desires for a massive
OL,10,Funilateral reduction in US support for
OL,11,FUkraine and his determination to
OL,12,Fimpose significant additional tariffs
OL,13,Fon Chinese and European exports.
OL,15,FTempering Trump's challenge to the
OL,16,FUK's security and prosperity may
OL,17,Frequire political skills above and
OL,18,Fbeyond those of a conventional
OL,19,Fdiplomat - Mandelson, to state the
OL,20,Fobvious, has that craft.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
