OL,3,CWhy Starmer picked Mandelson for
OL,4,CWashington
OL,6,FIn the words of one senior politician,
OL,7,Fwho is no friend of Mandelson, "Trump
OL,8,Flikes people he can make a connection
OL,9,Fwith - and Mandy is personable and
OL,10,Funderstands power and connections."
OL,12,FBut there are also risks, and not just
OL,13,Fthat Mandelson doesn't play golf.
OL,15,FOne of the big reasons Mandelson is
OL,16,Fexpert in trade issues is because he
OL,17,Fwas EU trade commissioner.
