OL,3,CWhy Starmer picked Mandelson for
OL,4,CWashington
OL,6,FHe is a great europhile, whereas Trump
OL,7,Fcalls the EU "mini China" and sees it
OL,8,Fas parasitic on the US economically
OL,9,Fand in respect of security.
OL,11,FAnother risk is that Mandelson has
OL,12,Fnever knowingly been self-deprecating
OL,13,For inconspicuous. He wears controversy
OL,14,Flike a designer coat and he's been
OL,15,Fsacked from government for it twice.
