OL,3,CWhy Starmer picked Mandelson for
OL,4,CWashington
OL,6,FIt is no anomaly that Mandelson was a
OL,7,Fshoo-in for this job earlier in the
OL,8,Fautumn, till he remarked that maybe
OL,9,FStarmer should use Farage's good
OL,10,Foffices to build a relationship with
OL,11,FTrump.
OL,13,FAccording to senior diplomats, that
OL,14,Fpublic suggestion did not endear
OL,15,Fhimself to Starmer and almost cost
OL,16,FMandelson the keys to the UK's
OL,17,Fmagnificent DC diplomatic residence.
OL,19,FBut Starmer, as is becoming his habit,
OL,20,Fhas made a bold call in appointing him.
