OL,3,CWhy Starmer picked Mandelson for
OL,4,CWashington
OL,6,FWhether it is the taxes he chooses to
OL,7,Fimpose or the money he chooses to
OL,8,Fwithhold from the vulnerable, the PM
OL,9,Fis not shying away from decisions that
OL,10,Fare neither populist or popular.
OL,12,FStarmer has also again manifested one
OL,13,Fof the big facts of his government,
OL,14,Fnamely the influence of his chief of
OL,15,Fstaff Morgan McSweeney, who was only
OL,16,Frecently schmoozing Trump's team in
OL,17,Fthe US.
